                    "text": "The \"Savitribai Phule Self-Help Scheme\", managed by the District Intermediate Cooperative Development Committee, supports women entrepreneurs from the SC category in Madhya Pradesh by offering margin money assistance of up to ₹15,000/- (50% of the project cost, with a maximum project cost of ₹50,000/-). This financial aid can help them start small businesses across various sectors."
