      "eligibilityCriteria": {
        "eligibilityDescription_md": "\n  - The applicant must be a woman.\n  -  The applicant must be a resident of Madhya Pradesh.\n  - The applicant must belong to the Scheduled Caste (SC) category.\n  - The applicant’s age should be between 18 to 55 years.\n  - The applicant must be literate.\n  - The applicant should be currently unemployed.\n  - The applicant must fall under the Below Poverty Line (BPL) category.\n  - The applicant should not have any outstanding defaults with any nationalized bank, cooperative bank, or other financial institution.\n\n",
